org.wcardinal.controller.data

Class SList<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.wcardinal.controller.data.SList<V>
  • Type Parameters:
    V - element type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<V>, java.util.Collection<V>, java.util.List<V>, SLockable, SVariable, Unlockable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SListImpl, SMovableList

    public abstract class SList<V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SLockable, SVariable, java.util.List<V>
    Represents the list data. The class V can be any class. However, for synchronization, the class V must be serializable to, and deserializable from JSON by the Jackson.
